option.STARS_ENABLED=Enable Stars
option.STARS_ENABLED.comment=Show stars in the night sky.

option.STAR_SCALE=Star Scale
option.STAR_SCALE.comment=Overall grid scale for star placement. Higher = smaller star patterns.

option.STAR_SIZE=Star Size
option.STAR_SIZE.comment=Size of individual stars. Higher = larger star points.

option.STAR_DENSITY=Star Density
option.STAR_DENSITY.comment=How many stars appear. Higher = denser star field.

option.STAR_BRIGHTNESS=Star Brightness
option.STAR_BRIGHTNESS.comment=Brightness of individual stars.

option.STAR_TWINKLE=Star Twinkle
option.STAR_TWINKLE.comment=How much stars flicker. 0 = steady, 1 = maximum twinkle.

option.STAR_SHOOTING_ENABLED=Shooting Stars
option.STAR_SHOOTING_ENABLED.comment=Occasional shooting stars streak across the night sky.

option.STAR_SHOOTING_BRIGHTNESS=Shooting Star Brightness
option.STAR_SHOOTING_BRIGHTNESS.comment=Brightness of shooting star trails.

