option.NIGHT_NEBULA_ENABLED=Enable Night Nebula
option.NIGHT_NEBULA_ENABLED.comment=Adds soft colored nebula clouds to the overworld night sky.

option.NIGHT_NEBULA_INTENSITY=Nebula Intensity
option.NIGHT_NEBULA_INTENSITY.comment=How bright/visible the nebula patches are.

option.NIGHT_NEBULA_SCALE=Nebula Scale
