option.VANILLA_CLOUD_L2_COVERAGE.comment=Cloud coverage for the middle (main) layer. Higher = more clouds.
option.VANILLA_CLOUD_L2_PIXEL_SIZE=Middle Pixel Size
option.VANILLA_CLOUD_L2_PIXEL_SIZE.comment=Grid cell size for the middle layer. Smaller = finer detail, larger = bigger cloud chunks.
option.VANILLA_CLOUD_L2_OPACITY=Middle Opacity
option.VANILLA_CLOUD_L2_OPACITY.comment=Opacity of the middle cloud layer. 0 = fully transparent, 100 = fully opaque.
