option.MATERIAL_REFLECTIONS_ENABLED.comment=Adds SSR reflections to polished stone, smooth stone, glazed terracotta, prismarine bricks, and other polished surfaces.

option.MATERIAL_REFLECTION_AMOUNT=Reflection Strength
option.MATERIAL_REFLECTION_AMOUNT.comment=How reflective the material surfaces are. Higher = stronger mirror-like reflections.

option.MATERIAL_REFLECTION_FRESNEL=Fresnel Strength
option.MATERIAL_REFLECTION_FRESNEL.comment=Boosts reflections at glancing angles (looking across the surface). Real materials reflect more at shallow angles.

# --- Leaf Sheen ---

screen.LEAF_SHEEN=Leaf Sheen
screen.LEAF_SHEEN.comment=Subsurface scattering and fresnel rim effects on leaf blocks for natural-looking foliage.

option.LEAF_SHEEN_ENABLED=Enable Leaf Sheen
option.LEAF_SHEEN_ENABLED.comment=Adds subsurface glow and fresnel rim highlights to leaf blocks for a lush, natural look.

option.LEAF_SSS_STRENGTH=SSS Strength
option.LEAF_SSS_STRENGTH.comment=Subsurface scattering: warm glow through back-lit leaves (sun shining through canopy).

option.LEAF_FRESNEL_STRENGTH=Fresnel Strength
option.LEAF_FRESNEL_STRENGTH.comment=Bright rim at grazing viewing angles, like a waxy sheen on leaf edges.

option.LEAF_SHADOW_TRANSMITTANCE=Shadow Transmittance
option.LEAF_SHADOW_TRANSMITTANCE.comment=Subtle light leak onto back faces of leaves in shadow. 0 = no leak.

option.LEAF_SHADOW_SOFTNESS=Shadow Softness
option.LEAF_SHADOW_SOFTNESS.comment=How much to blur shadows on leaf blocks. Higher values soften shadow edges, hiding the blocky leaf geometry for a more natural look.

# --- Glass Filter ---

screen.GLASS_FILTER=Glass Filter
screen.GLASS_FILTER.comment=Stained-glass color filtering that tints everything seen through colored glass.

option.GLASS_FILTER_ENABLED=Glass Color Enforcement
option.GLASS_FILTER_ENABLED.comment=Tints everything seen through glass using the glass color (stained-glass style). Not just an overlay.

option.GLASS_FILTER_STRENGTH=Filter Strength
option.GLASS_FILTER_STRENGTH.comment=Overall strength of the glass color enforcement.

option.GLASS_FILTER_ENFORCEMENT=Filter Enforcement
option.GLASS_FILTER_ENFORCEMENT.comment=0 = subtle multiply, 1 = strong luminance-based color enforcement.

option.GLASS_FILTER_SATURATION=Filter Saturation
option.GLASS_FILTER_SATURATION.comment=Boosts saturation of the glass tint color used for filtering.

# --- Fake Terrain ---

screen.FAKE_TERRAIN=Fake Terrain
screen.FAKE_TERRAIN.comment=Fills the void beyond loaded chunks with a flat ground plane for a less empty horizon.

option.FAKE_TERRAIN_ENABLED=Enable Fake Terrain
option.FAKE_TERRAIN_ENABLED.comment=Renders a flat ground plane beyond loaded chunks to fill the void at the horizon.

option.FAKE_TERRAIN_Y=Ground Level (Y)
