option.CG_SPLIT_TONING_ENABLED.comment=Adds separate color tinting to dark areas (shadows) and bright areas (highlights).

option.CG_SPLIT_TONING_INTENSITY=Intensity
option.CG_SPLIT_TONING_INTENSITY.comment=Overall strength of the split toning effect. 0 = off, 1 = full color.

option.CG_SPLIT_TONING_BALANCE=Balance
option.CG_SPLIT_TONING_BALANCE.comment=Shifts the toning toward shadows or highlights. -1 = shadow heavy, 0 = balanced, 1 = highlight heavy.

screen.CG_SHADOW_COLOR=Shadow Tint Color
