option.CG_POSTERIZE_ENABLED.comment=Limits color levels for a stylized flat-color appearance.

option.CG_POSTERIZE_LEVELS=Color Levels
option.CG_POSTERIZE_LEVELS.comment=Number of color levels per channel. Lower = more stylized (3 = comic book, 16+ = subtle).

option.CG_POSTERIZE_DITHER=Dithering
option.CG_POSTERIZE_DITHER.comment=Adds noise to reduce visible color banding between posterized levels.

