screen.END_VOID_EVENT_SETTINGS=Void Event
screen.END_VOID_EVENT_SETTINGS.comment=Cinematic sky event cycle. The vortex periodically implodes into darkness, then explodes back with a cosmic eye opening at its center.

option.END_EVENT_ENABLED=Enable Void Event
option.END_EVENT_ENABLED.comment=Cinematic End sky event. Every few minutes the vortex accelerates, implodes into total darkness, then explodes back like a Big Bang with shockwave rings and a cosmic eye.

option.END_EVENT_CYCLE=Cycle Duration
