option.END_EVENT_EYE_ENABLED=Enable Vortex Eye
option.END_EVENT_EYE_ENABLED.comment=After the Big Bang explosion, a cosmic eye opens at the vortex center, stares at you, blinks, then closes.

screen.END_EVENT_EYE_COLOR=Eye Iris Color
screen.END_EVENT_EYE_COLOR.comment=Color of the cosmic eye's iris that appears after the Big Bang.

